<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_83d12ec2-9b1f-419f-8069-81ba32c7b5e8" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>E1D6</sptc><title id="_f209c3cd-8e08-4ef5-b5c1-2f31363fcbab">Where sprinklers are required: Class 2 and 3 buildings other than residential care buildings</title><archive-num/><clause-variation href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/10625_0.3.0.xml" variation="VIC" variation-type="REPLACE">VIC REPLACE Clause</clause-variation><subclause id="_55df51c2-e33d-435d-8a10-d15c14a0cf55" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_30ffa997-5bd4-4167-872b-9f0d443302a7">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>In a Class 2 or 3 building, or any multi-classified building containing a Class 2 or 3 part, sprinklers are <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_5e975fd3-8605-42c8-a23f-b65edd14168e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> throughout the whole building if any part of the building has—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_882a28f0-31db-4c6d-9745-84cf208c3c29">a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1439_5.1.0.xml#_7023b962-6482-412b-8416-ab1d9016072b" id="_b1ace8fb-c1ef-4a73-a371-217cf4ec5062" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">rise in storeys</xref> of 4 or more; and</li><li id="_5e93fa66-f07a-48bd-b104-bcbdac00f675">an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1252_2.0.0.xml#_cd986c21-bc64-43a9-954d-86e35d335b74" id="_07e43218-be35-41d7-9a95-7210669bdb0a" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">effective height</xref> of not more than 25 m.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_8ea44a72-9162-4180-b5b6-660223f883a3" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_154f1c38-47db-4875-a125-502a465da9c3">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>The requirements of (1) do not apply to—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_d15bd68a-b9ab-4011-850d-112485b94427">a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1436_4.0.0.xml#_b286ccd1-342e-49e1-95e9-4b6a0a6c0447" id="_5ff3dfb4-502e-4751-922e-c791b228332a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">residential care building</xref>; and</li><li id="_0a430f87-0852-4463-8079-142a703dfc8e">a Class 8 <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1255_0.4.0.xml#_7a37df1f-0b8b-4b03-94ca-69ea423a363f" id="_d2873707-5abb-4151-9ceb-60c70dcb8bf5" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">electricity network substation</xref> with a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1314_2.10.0.xml#_7da927fe-453e-424f-b6ec-280f4e464397" id="_f44a09a9-679b-4be2-b94f-e345dac75ab9" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">floor area</xref> not more than 200 m<sup id="_a5c87c98-e63a-404e-9776-ce539c931f7b">2</sup> located within a multi-classified building.</li></ol></subclause></clause>